        "gghyMeQcXQQ_text": "<p>Mike Jones</p>",
        "ggkoiQzyn6h_text": "Success stories",
        "gglk2xgpN5W_text": "<p>“My beard used to itch nonstop and shed flakes everywhere. Within a week of using this cream, the irritation calmed down and the flakes stopped. Now it’s part of my daily routine.”</p>",
        "ggn4JK2wcJy_text": "<p>Camellia oil penetrates deep into the hair shaft, reducing protein loss and leaving beard and scalp hair stronger, shinier, and more resilient.</p>",
        "ggnHhhfM2V8_text": "<p>Rich in antioxidants and natural emollients, it helps maintain the skin’s natural barrier. The defense line samurai unknowingly relied on against irritation and infection.</p>",
        "ggsbdLHaKo6_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#161723;\"><strong>Published:</strong></span> Sunday, August 24, 2025</p>",
